            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Add the<strong> pickled red cabbage </strong>and<strong> grated carrot</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>mayo</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy red cabbage slaw</strong></p>",
